Usage: setOutboundReport [-help] -delay {early late both}
                         [-filename_prefix <string>]
                         [-report_constant_nets {true false}]
                         [-type {lower upper both}]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-delay {early late both}               # Control whether extrapolation
                                       # information is to be shown for min or
                                       # max (or both) analyses (enum, required)
-filename_prefix <string>              # Specify the prefix to be used in the
                                       # name(s) of the report file(s)
                                       # (string, optional)
-report_constant_nets {true false}     # Control whether extrapolation
                                       # information is to be shown for
                                       # constant nets or not (enum, optional)
-type {lower upper both}               # Control whether extrapolation
                                       # information is to be shown for lower
                                       # or upper(or both) outbound slews
                                       # (enum, optional)